3	//! Each fixture is an OBSERVED oracle WARNING topic block (extracted from the
4	//! round-6 reference targets, cross-checked with the constructed probes
5	//! lhs1/lhs2/lhs3/pc1/pc2 in round6/probes). We build the matching AST by hand
6	//! and assert byte-for-byte reproduction of the affected topic block.
